data.description: This stunning 4 Bedroom 3 Bath pool home in Waterset is found in a unique planned community offering its residents numerous amenities! PAID OFF SOLAR AND TESLA POWERWALLS!!!!  18 INCH TILE THROUGHOUT, NO CARPET!!!!!  With a spacious open concept floorplan you will find room to spread out and entertain as you continue outside to the pool. The soaring tray ceilings and tons of natural light make the homeowner appreciate the good things in life.  The gourmet kitchen has been outfitted with GE Cafe appliances for the at home chef that has everything. Gorgeous granite counters, wood cabinetry, stainless steel appliances and a 5-burner gas cooktop are just a few items found in this breath taking kitchen.  A huge center island allows friends and family to interact while meals are being prepared. The large master retreat features tray ceilings, a walk-in closet, a large walk in shower and a vanity with dual sinks. This split floor plan also offers 3 generously sized secondary bedrooms and 2 full secondary baths. The windows in the front of the home are high impact windows and there are hurricane shutters stored in the garage. A spacious laundry - mud room area transitions to the 2-car garage. The solar panel system comes with two 13 kw Tesla Powerwalls. The system could save you approximately $250 per month on your monthly electric bill. If power goes out, the Tesla Powerwalls could power the residence for approximately 24hrs if fully charged. The backyard is fully fenced in. Waterset's resort-style amenities include pools, waterslides, splash pad, clubhouse, pickleball, playgrounds, parks, planned events and more. Let us introduce you to Florida living at it's finest!
